        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "些须小事，就该与我送了吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，死鬼末好送，活鬼么哪哼送得脱介？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勿要肝经火旺，替唔跌两记背罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姑母、陈妙常同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转过荷香径，又来丹桂阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，姑奶奶来哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽闻长叹语，使我更关心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦，格个宝贝倒也来个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，侄儿，这两日病体如何了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "越发沉重了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更加勿是哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，潘相公，吉人自有天相，料然无事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！是哪个讲话？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是俚哉㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙常徒弟，在此看你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拉笃格搭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀，有劳吓有劳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "相公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好仔勒谢还来得及个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿，你把起病根由，说与我知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘，一言难尽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格叫哑子吃黄连，说勿出个苦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （山坡羊） 这病儿何曾经害，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这病儿好难担代。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这病儿好似雨过花羞态。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我难摆开、姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心头便怎么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （山坡羊） 心头去复来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄昏梦断，梦断天涯外。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我心事难提泪满腮。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈妙常哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勿关唔啥事，为啥了哭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （山坡羊） 伤怀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是风寒上起的？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （山坡羊） 不为风寒眼倦开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "堪哀、姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是忧愁上起的？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘必正 （山坡羊） 只为忧愁头懒抬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑母 （山坡羊） 莫不是害了些王仲宣登楼无奈？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公阿是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勿是个。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑母 （山坡羊） 莫不是染了些楚三闾江潭流派？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公阿是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也勿是个。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑母 （山坡羊） 莫不是渴中山病儿转深？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才勿是个。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑母 （山坡羊） 莫不是赴高唐酬孽债？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿呀我好恨呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好钝吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （山坡羊） 你休恨来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜明珠打哈欠，宝贝开口哉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （山坡羊） 愁肠须摆开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑奶奶，阿曾吃饭拉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （山坡羊） 月圆月缺，月有盈亏害，"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿要泡壶茶唔吃？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格么替唔跌两记背罢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这倒使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （山坡羊） 岂可人无一日灾？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "格两日殿上烧香个阿多？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔革响里是健个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒也安逸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈妙常 （山坡羊） 襟怀，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你把那段心儿且放开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一条百脚！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑母 （山坡羊） 书斋，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好听春雷天上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侄儿，恐佛殿上有人来烧香，我去看看就来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姑娘请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘相公，还是服药为上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！吃什么药？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心病还将心药医，"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休将闲口惹是非。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因闲口生心病，"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿冤家早脱离！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我奉太上老君急急如律令敕！妖怪速退！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姑母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈妙常",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖，来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姑母、陈妙常同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，好笑我俚相公，直梗病重，听见说陈姑来哉，看俚直立个立起来，说道"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳吓有劳！几乎跌下去。吖，让我来开开俚个心看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，相公，相公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，吓……正欲朦胧睡去，什么大惊小怪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才我送姑奶奶出去，看见陈姑格张小嘴，对仔我一扭，我就明白哉，走得上"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去。陈姑说道：吓，进安哥，你家相公的病我都晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖她竟晓得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才晓得个呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她便怎么说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俚说我有绝妙的方儿，管教一服就好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！是她说的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是俚说个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖，待我就去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（潘必正嗽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，格付样式，哪好去介？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是吓，待我除下帕儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解脱仔包头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卸了裙儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脱落仔格裙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（潘必正嗽。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公，唔到落里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到陈姑房中，写方儿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进安",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啥人说个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘必正",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
